text: "Stranger in Town" is a 1984 song by American rock band Toto and is the leading single from their fifth studio album Isolation. It went to number 30 in the United States, number 100 in the United Kingdom, number 16 in Canada and number 40 in Australia. It also went to number 7 on the Billboard Mainstream Rock chart. == References == Category:1984 songs Category:Toto (band) songs Category:Synth rock songs
